rows.label: tlk01000804_msg0001
rows.name:
What should I do...
The girl I'm imagining is too cute.

rows.label: tlk01000804_msg0002
rows.name:
I wish she were real...
If I went on an adventure like
Rex-niichan, maybe I could meet her...

rows.label: tlk01000804_msg0003
rows.name:
Why are you worried?
This is studying, isn't it?

rows.label: tlk01000804_msg0101
rows.name:
The teacher said it would be good to
use someone close to me as an example, but...

rows.label: tlk01000804_msg0102
rows.name:
I don't have a mom or dad...
So I guess it would be Auntie Correl.

rows.label: tlk01000804_msg0201
rows.name:
Having a Nopon teacher is
so cute.

rows.label: tlk01000804_msg0202
rows.name:
Kurukuru-san comes to the village sometimes,
but a Nopon has never lived here, so this is the first time
I've been able to watch one for so long.

rows.label: tlk01000804_msg0203
rows.name:
Teacher Lapupu really likes
cute things!
